  07 Apr 2013; Ulrich Müller <ulm@gentoo.org> helpblocks-1.21-r1.ebuild:
  RESTRICT="mirror bindist" since distribution is not allowed, bug 464768.

  05 Feb 2013; Tim Harder <radhermit@gentoo.org> metadata.xml:
  Use herd instead of maintainer for metadata.

  05 Sep 2012; Justin Lecher <jlec@gentoo.org> helpblocks-1.21-r1.ebuild:
  Use domenu instead insinto + doins to install .desktop files

  17 Apr 2012; Ryan Hill <dirtyepic@gentoo.org> metadata.xml:
  Set wxwidgets as maintainer.

  06 Apr 2012; Pacho Ramos <pacho@gentoo.org> metadata.xml:
  Drop maintainer due retirement, bug #63588

  29 Mar 2011; Christoph Mende <angelos@gentoo.org> helpblocks-1.21-r1.ebuild:
  Fixed slot deps

